title: Pranjul Garg
text:
With a year of hands-on experience as a Business Analyst, I specialize in delivering efficient, data-driven solutions. Passionate about continuous learning, I combine my expertise in Microsoft Excel, Power BI, Python, and R to transform data into actionable insights.
My background in software development and analysis enables me to solve complex problems with innovative solutions. I’m eager to leverage my technical and analytical skills to drive business success in Analyst roles.
